data.description: This impressive property is located off one of the most beautiful paved country roads in Texas. This amazing home has 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths with flex room. Cross fenced pasture area surrounded by beautiful pine trees. The middle  section is forest for hunting. The back property line has a running water creek. Huge metal building, roll up door for tractors with elect/lights and concrete floor. Landscaped entry with moss rock, roses and sage that compliment a well made, self-locking pipe gate on. Gorgeous Red Tea rose garden across front of home that is amazing with the white brick. The main areas are wood tile that will last a lifetime. The main living area has high ceiling, huge stone fireplace. This home has two water heaters, two living areas(game room/flex) and a kitchen, plenty of useable counter space, gas stove/oven. The back porch is  private  and surrounded by trees. Sunsets are amazing from the porch. The backyard has a mini Stonehenge fire pit. Come see Home, Sweet Home.
